rComments: ugh. the class i took with her was easy but she sucked at teaching it.
Take the independent research class with her. I met with her twice, wrote ONE 12 page paper (that's it!), and got an A in the class.

Teacher was unclear and unhelpful in assignments. Expected everyone to know what she meant. On papers, her comments were incongruous with the grade given (ie-only good comments, but a lower grade.) She often let class run over, making me late for another class. I'm not even sure how she got a degree
Teacher had no techonological knowledge. Asked questions with a specific answer in mind and was not very receptive to different interpretations.
